378
00:16:48,470 --> 00:16:49,320
Then I found out

379
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,910
you were the biggest loser among us.

380
00:17:05,520 --> 00:17:06,560
What secrets?

381
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:07,920
Tell me.

382
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:18,280
I saw you sucked up to the Chief Minister all the time.

383
00:17:18,590 --> 00:17:19,520
It's understandable.

384
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,470
But his wife

385
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:25,310
