386
00:17:25,310 --> 00:17:27,070
Why hooked up with her?

387
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:30,110
You're not doing this to pry into the secrets of

388
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:31,470
the Office of Justice, right?

389
00:17:32,310 --> 00:17:33,110
Cheers.

