411
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:33,560
That's all?

412
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:36,350
That's all for now.

413
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:56,070
All right, Zhao Buyou.

414
00:18:56,070 --> 00:18:58,400
You asked me here in the middle of the night.

415
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:02,000
If that's what you want to talk about,

416
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:04,070
