00:19:23,470 --> 00:19:24,520
You were the one

423
00:19:24,710 --> 00:19:25,880
to hire those pirates, right?

424
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,520
Fifteen years later,

425
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:28,590
you arranged the Auspicious Sign

426
00:19:28,590 --> 00:19:31,070
over the Bian River to cause confusion among the people.

427
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:33,710
The problem is, why would a prosecutor like you

428
00:19:33,710 --> 00:19:35,160
