434
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,350
Now die!

435
00:19:50,350 --> 00:19:51,680
So I was right.

436
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:00,710
Unsheathe your sword.

437
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:05,880
A scribe who got fired by his superior

438
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:08,680
