439
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:11,230
This is a felony.

440
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:12,760
Take him away.

441
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:13,590
Tie him up.

442
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:16,160
Don't move!

443
00:20:17,070 --> 00:20:19,190
The Office of Treasury is colluding with the Office of Miscellaneous Purchases.

444
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:23,110
Am I correct?

445
00:20:23,350 --> 00:20:26,280
I heard Mr. Di is about to be transferred there.

446
00:20:26,280 --> 00:20:28,000
A fat job at the Office of Treasury.

447
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:29,560
The man behind you

448
00:20:29,560 --> 00:20:30,830
