449
00:20:32,160 --> 00:20:34,160
transfer to the Office of Treasury, right?

450
00:20:34,430 --> 00:20:35,920
Keep dreaming.

451
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:38,000
That position was taken yesterday.

452
00:20:41,640 --> 00:20:42,470
Really?

453
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,640
You don't believe me?

454
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:47,000
I have evidence with me.

455
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:47,800
It's in my pocket.

456
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:50,400
Let me take a look.

457
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:55,320
The man who took the job yesterday

458
00:20:55,520 --> 00:20:57,400
has ordered some umbrellas

459
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:58,270
in my wife's shop.

460
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,830
We have his signature.

461
00:21:00,080 --> 00:21:00,830
If you don't believe me,

462
00:21:00,830 --> 00:21:01,550
go ask around.

