509
00:25:28,430 --> 00:25:30,000
You want to know the truth?

510
00:25:31,560 --> 00:25:32,800
Let me tell you this.

511
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:35,190
Even I don't know about the truth!

512
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:39,310
