554
00:27:30,310 --> 00:27:31,190
Who are their name?

555
00:27:59,470 --> 00:28:00,160
Di Lun.

556
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:02,040
Release my wife!

557
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:10,710
