577
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:09,110
I'd secretly move my hands there.

578
00:29:10,230 --> 00:29:12,310
I was waiting for you to put down the tool.

579
00:29:13,350 --> 00:29:15,470
If I got lucky, I'd touch your hand.

580
00:29:17,800 --> 00:29:19,160
I was thinking

581
00:29:20,110 --> 00:29:23,110
it would be wonderful if I could hold her hands for the rest of our lives.

582
00:29:25,110 --> 00:29:25,880
Now

583
00:29:26,920 --> 00:29:28,880
over ten years have passed.

584
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:30,880
Honey.

585
00:29:33,000 --> 00:29:34,430
If afterlife truly exists,

586
00:29:35,950 --> 00:29:36,830
in our next life,

587
00:29:37,590 --> 00:29:38,560
and the life after that,

588
00:29:39,640 --> 00:29:40,950
let's be together again, all right?

589
00:29:40,950 --> 00:29:42,070
Enough! That's not the time

590
00:29:42,070 --> 00:29:43,400
for this.

591
00:29:43,950 --> 00:29:45,160
Do you want to die here?

592
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:46,190
Promise me.

593
00:29:47,070 --> 00:29:48,280
Let's be together again, all right.

594
00:29:48,560 --> 00:29:49,070
All right.

595
00:29:53,400 --> 00:29:54,590
Gu Zhen!

596
00:29:56,040 --> 00:29:58,110
