597
00:29:58,680 --> 00:29:59,280
Who's that?

598
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:00,950
Inspector Gu?

599
00:30:00,950 --> 00:30:01,520
Right!

600
00:30:02,520 --> 00:30:03,710
Gu Zhen!

601
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:06,230
