602
00:30:10,430 --> 00:30:11,310
Zhao Buyou!

603
00:30:11,560 --> 00:30:12,590
Judge Wan.

604
00:30:12,590 --> 00:30:13,560
Hurry up!

605
00:30:14,310 --> 00:30:16,430
Judge Wan, what took you so long?

606
00:30:16,800 --> 00:30:17,800
He didn't say

607
