608
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,190
Hurry!

609
00:30:23,710 --> 00:30:24,520
Let's go!

610
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:35,520
Slowly.

611
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,400
Over here.

612
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:39,070
All right.

613
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:41,230
Just put it there.

614
00:30:42,950 --> 00:30:43,760
Zhao Buyou.

615
00:30:45,920 --> 00:30:48,160
