625
00:31:25,800 --> 00:31:26,760
What's this? You...

626
00:31:26,760 --> 00:31:28,040
Hang on a second.

627
00:31:28,590 --> 00:31:29,230
Inspector Gu.

628
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:31,920
Can we have a moment?

629
00:31:34,310 --> 00:31:35,310
Let's talk right here.

630
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:39,400
All right.

631
00:31:40,710 --> 00:31:41,950
We're all allies now.

632
00:31:43,950 --> 00:31:44,760
Inspector Gu.

633
00:31:45,350 --> 00:31:47,680
Do you even know who's behind me?

634
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:49,880
You said who's behind you?

635
00:31:52,590 --> 00:31:53,880
Isn't it Wan Fu?

636
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:54,560
Yeah.

637
00:31:55,590 --> 00:31:56,160
It's me.

638
00:31:57,190 --> 00:31:58,920
Judge Wan, please don't joke about it.

639
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:02,590
I know

640
00:32:03,280 --> 00:32:05,190
I've done many things wrong for all these years.

641
00:32:05,950 --> 00:32:07,040
But I've decided

642
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:10,430
to tell you who's behind me

643
00:32:10,950 --> 00:32:12,760
and all the dirty work I've done

644
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:14,920
for him for all these years,

645
00:32:15,400 --> 00:32:16,350
every last bit of it,

646
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:17,920
including the case

647
00:32:17,920 --> 00:32:20,000
concerning Li Yan fifteen years ago.

648
00:32:20,430 --> 00:32:21,280
How about this?

649
00:32:21,590 --> 00:32:23,800
You and I cooperate to take him down.

650
00:32:24,190 --> 00:32:24,800
You agree?

651
00:32:25,760 --> 00:32:27,830
So you were the one

652
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:29,800
who killed Li Yan?

653
00:32:34,470 --> 00:32:35,280
That's correct.

654
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:54,040
Is this?

655
00:32:54,350 --> 00:32:56,070
Member of the Jingyuan Triumphant Army,

656
00:32:56,070 --> 00:32:56,760
Gu Zhen.

657
00:32:57,760 --> 00:32:59,950
And the Commander of the same army

658
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:01,470
is Li Yan.

659
00:33:56,710 --> 00:33:57,520
It's right here.

660
00:34:10,710 --> 00:34:12,360
It's been fifteen years.

661
00:34:15,870 --> 00:34:18,910
I've been looking for you for fifteen years.

662
00:34:21,950 --> 00:34:23,080
Go to hell

663
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:27,470
and apologize to my brother.

664
00:34:30,040 --> 00:34:31,430
Gu Zhen

665
00:34:33,600 --> 00:34:34,390
of the Jingyuan Triumphant Army

666
00:34:37,390 --> 00:34:41,470
has avenged the Commander

667
00:34:44,910 --> 00:34:49,230
Li Yan!

668
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:23,430
Wen Yue.

669
00:35:30,360 --> 00:35:31,950
How did you get away?

670
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:37,360
Li Yan's a good official.

671
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:39,600
I couldn't bring myself to do it.

672
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:41,320
Our employer told me

673
00:35:42,320 --> 00:35:43,520
to kill them all,

674
00:35:44,150 --> 00:35:45,320
