675
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:47,390
Kill them!

676
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:50,230
Kill them!

677
00:35:51,950 --> 00:35:52,470
Kill them!

678
00:36:02,120 --> 00:36:02,910
Kill him!

679
00:36:09,150 --> 00:36:10,470
We'll talk about it later.

680
00:36:13,470 --> 00:36:14,360
It's the Office of Justice.

681
00:36:14,360 --> 00:36:14,870
They are here.

682
00:36:14,870 --> 00:36:15,800
We're here for an investigation.

683
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:17,430
You've been surrounded.

684
00:36:17,520 --> 00:36:18,560
Surrender now!

685
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:19,710
Later, those people from the Office of Justice arrived.

686
00:36:20,430 --> 00:36:22,470
They told us to surrender

687
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:24,560
while shooting arrows at us.

688
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:27,520
In a moment of despair, I jumped into the water and went ashore.

689
00:36:27,760 --> 00:36:29,000
That's how I got away.

690
00:36:30,600 --> 00:36:32,040
When he died,

691
00:36:33,950 --> 00:36:35,150
did he suffer?

692
00:36:36,710 --> 00:36:37,520
It happened

693
00:36:38,710 --> 00:36:39,520
in the blink of an eye.

694
00:36:42,430 --> 00:36:43,670
Inspector Gu.

695
00:36:45,470 --> 00:36:46,870
What do you plan to deal with us?

696
00:36:47,870 --> 00:36:48,870
With laws?

697
00:36:50,150 --> 00:36:51,080
Or morality?

698
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:08,320
I'll come see you one day.

699
00:37:30,190 --> 00:37:31,000
Let's go.

700
00:37:38,520 --> 00:37:39,670
You seemed tough

701
00:37:39,670 --> 00:37:41,390
when you wrote the divorce letter.

702
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:44,470
"I wish you a life of happiness."

703
00:37:46,040 --> 00:37:47,040
So I came to your rescue.

704
00:37:47,040 --> 00:37:47,760
Happy now?

705
00:37:48,520 --> 00:37:49,670
I swear to Heaven,

706
00:37:49,670 --> 00:37:51,430
I sincerely hoped you could leave.

707
00:37:52,120 --> 00:37:53,840
I wanted Gu Zhen

708
00:37:54,230 --> 00:37:55,600
to arrest that scumbag.

709
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:58,150
