712
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,000
Let's go.

713
00:38:11,560 --> 00:38:12,320
Go home.

714
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:14,520
Honey.

715
00:38:14,910 --> 00:38:16,000
I've been thinking about it for a while,

716
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:17,560
