717
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:35,190
You said,

718
00:38:35,630 --> 00:38:38,190
as long as we're living people, we won't starve to death in East Capital.

719
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:39,840
Is it true?

720
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,120
Of course.

721
00:38:44,430 --> 00:38:45,560
So you're not leaving?

722
00:38:46,950 --> 00:38:47,670
I'm staying.

723
00:38:53,630 --> 00:38:54,710
Please help me up.

724
00:39:07,430 --> 00:39:09,120
Zhao Buyou, wake up.

725
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:11,470
Hang in there, we're home.

726
00:39:22,150 --> 00:39:24,190
If you still feel dizzy and nauseous,

727
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:25,910
