728
00:39:29,830 --> 00:39:30,600
Honey.

729
00:39:32,870 --> 00:39:34,590
Am I too much of a wimp?

730
00:39:36,120 --> 00:39:39,270
I'm a grown man in my late thirties.

731
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:42,120
Yet it almost scared me to death.

732
00:39:42,950 --> 00:39:44,560
I can't even begin to imagine

733
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:46,560
how you pulled through

734
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,710
while you were still in your teens.

735
00:40:07,670 --> 00:40:09,000
But rest assured.

736
00:40:10,870 --> 00:40:12,670
Di Lun is dead.

737
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:14,670
No one can prove it now.

738
00:40:16,080 --> 00:40:17,150
As for Inspector Gu,

739
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:21,080
he dared take such a great risk

740
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:24,390
just to avenge a fellow soldier.

741
00:40:24,760 --> 00:40:26,950
I think he's a man of integrity.

742
00:40:27,870 --> 00:40:29,950
He won't be coming for us.

743
00:40:31,390 --> 00:40:33,670
I'm worried about your fellow disciple, though.

744
00:40:34,910 --> 00:40:36,120
Yishui is

745
00:40:37,950 --> 00:40:39,560
